title: Denali National Park & Preserve: The Wilderness Act Anniversary Litter
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Sled Dog Kennels     Meet the Sled Dogs     The Wilderness Act Anniversary Litter                The Wilderness Act Anniversary Litter         NPS Photo  Zahnie (m) Born: 8/09/2014  Zahnie was the only puppy in his litter, also known as a “singleton”. As an only child, he was incredibly spoiled because he did not have to compete with brothers and sisters for food or attention. Zahnie is incredibly sweet and is showing signs that he will be a great leader in the future.
